[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 0.0,
    "duration": 1.976
  },
  {
    "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]",
    "start": 1.976,
    "duration": 3.952
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 5.928,
    "duration": 27.172
  },
  {
    "text": "About the year A.D. 30,\noutside the walls of Jerusalem,",
    "start": 33.1,
    "duration": 4.85
  },
  {
    "text": "an extraordinary man\nnamed Jesus of Nazareth",
    "start": 37.95,
    "duration": 4.09
  },
  {
    "text": "was cruelly executed\nalong with two thieves.",
    "start": 42.04,
    "duration": 5.16
  },
  {
    "text": "It was an event that\nwould change the world,",
    "start": 47.2,
    "duration": 5.14
  },
  {
    "text": "and very few understood.",
    "start": 52.34,
    "duration": 2.25
  },
  {
    "text": "If thou be Christ,\nsave thyself and us.",
    "start": 54.59,
    "duration": 6.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Dost not thou fear\nGod, seeing thou art",
    "start": 60.93,
    "duration": 2.75
  },
  {
    "text": "in the same condemnation?",
    "start": 63.68,
    "duration": 2.39
  },
  {
    "text": "And we indeed justly; for\nwe receive the due reward",
    "start": 66.07,
    "duration": 4.41
  },
  {
    "text": "of our deeds: but this man\nhath done nothing amiss.",
    "start": 70.48,
    "duration": 6.09
  },
  {
    "text": "My name is John.",
    "start": 76.57,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "And indeed, it could be\nwell said of this man Jesus,",
    "start": 79.89,
    "duration": 4.528
  },
  {
    "text": "He did nothing amiss.",
    "start": 84.418,
    "duration": 4.812
  },
  {
    "text": "I was with Him for the\nlast years of His life.",
    "start": 89.23,
    "duration": 4.89
  },
  {
    "text": "I watched Him give\nsight to the blind,",
    "start": 94.12,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "heal the sick and the lame.",
    "start": 98.08,
    "duration": 3.76
  },
  {
    "text": "I was a witness as He raised\nthe dead back to life.",
    "start": 101.84,
    "duration": 4.78
  },
  {
    "text": "[SPEAKING ARAMAIC]",
    "start": 106.62,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "Talitha cumi.",
    "start": 107.6,
    "duration": 0.98
  },
  {
    "text": "[WOMAN CRYING]",
    "start": 108.58,
    "duration": 1.95
  },
  {
    "text": "Arise.",
    "start": 110.53,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 111.03,
    "duration": 15.71
  },
  {
    "text": "And yet He was\nrejected by those who",
    "start": 126.74,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "should have rejoiced\nat His coming.",
    "start": 130.16,
    "duration": 2.2
  },
  {
    "text": "What think ye?",
    "start": 132.36,
    "duration": 0.83
  },
  {
    "text": "He is guilty of death.",
    "start": 133.19,
    "duration": 1.992
  },
  {
    "text": "[ALL SPEAKING]",
    "start": 135.182,
    "duration": 0.583
  },
  {
    "text": "Death!",
    "start": 135.765,
    "duration": 0.499
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 136.264,
    "duration": 5.016
  },
  {
    "text": "As I and my fellow\ndisciples followed Him",
    "start": 141.28,
    "duration": 3.46
  },
  {
    "text": "through the cities\nand hills of Judea,",
    "start": 144.74,
    "duration": 2.99
  },
  {
    "text": "we came to know for\nourselves a miraculous truth",
    "start": 147.73,
    "duration": 5.752
  },
  {
    "text": "that the Apostle Peter\nexpressed for us all:",
    "start": 153.482,
    "duration": 3.388
  },
  {
    "text": "Whom do men say that\nI the Son of man am?",
    "start": 156.87,
    "duration": 2.992
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 159.862,
    "duration": 3.798
  },
  {
    "text": "Thou art the Christ, the\nSon of the living God.",
    "start": 163.66,
    "duration": 8.05
  },
  {
    "text": "The Christ, the Anointed One,\nhad the power and authority",
    "start": 171.71,
    "duration": 6.22
  },
  {
    "text": "to forgive mankind\nof their sins.",
    "start": 177.93,
    "duration": 3.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Son, thy sins be forgiven thee.",
    "start": 181.03,
    "duration": 2.99
  },
  {
    "text": "Arise.",
    "start": 184.02,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 184.52,
    "duration": 9.29
  },
  {
    "text": "In our possession, we had the\nwritings of ancient prophets",
    "start": 193.81,
    "duration": 3.795
  },
  {
    "text": "who prophesied about this\nMessiah, the Son of God,",
    "start": 197.605,
    "duration": 4.785
  },
  {
    "text": "but we did not fully comprehend.",
    "start": 202.39,
    "duration": 3.88
  },
  {
    "text": "For the last week of His\nlife, I was an eyewitness.",
    "start": 206.27,
    "duration": 5.42
  },
  {
    "text": "As the prophet Zechariah\nforetold centuries before,",
    "start": 211.69,
    "duration": 3.62
  },
  {
    "text": "many welcomed His\nreturn to Jerusalem",
    "start": 215.31,
    "duration": 2.92
  },
  {
    "text": "as the Messiah, their King.",
    "start": 218.23,
    "duration": 5.26
  },
  {
    "text": "As we dined with Him\non His last night,",
    "start": 223.49,
    "duration": 4.18
  },
  {
    "text": "He tried to warn and prepare\nus for His impending death.",
    "start": 227.67,
    "duration": 4.34
  },
  {
    "text": "A new commandment\nI give unto you,",
    "start": 232.01,
    "duration": 4.09
  },
  {
    "text": "That ye love one another,\nas I have loved you.",
    "start": 236.1,
    "duration": 6.05
  },
  {
    "text": "Greater love hath\nno man than this,",
    "start": 242.15,
    "duration": 3.31
  },
  {
    "text": "that he lay down his\nlife for his friends.",
    "start": 245.46,
    "duration": 2.35
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 247.81,
    "duration": 2.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Ye are my friends.",
    "start": 250.35,
    "duration": 1.975
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 252.325,
    "duration": 3.015
  },
  {
    "text": "Take this, and divide it among\nyourselves: for I say unto you,",
    "start": 255.34,
    "duration": 7.17
  },
  {
    "text": "I will not drink of\nthe fruit of the vine",
    "start": 262.51,
    "duration": 1.71
  },
  {
    "text": "until the kingdom\nof God shall come.",
    "start": 264.22,
    "duration": 3.57
  },
  {
    "text": "As we left this upper room,\nJesus was greatly troubled,",
    "start": 267.79,
    "duration": 4.86
  },
  {
    "text": "yet He spoke to us\nwords of comfort.",
    "start": 272.65,
    "duration": 2.908
  },
  {
    "text": "Peace I leave with you,\nmy peace I give unto you:",
    "start": 275.558,
    "duration": 6.592
  },
  {
    "text": "not as the world\ngiveth, give I unto you.",
    "start": 282.15,
    "duration": 1.95
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 284.1,
    "duration": 3.78
  },
  {
    "text": "Let not your heart be troubled,\nneither let it be afraid.",
    "start": 287.88,
    "duration": 6.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Still, we did not\nunderstand what lay ahead.",
    "start": 294.75,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 298.43,
    "duration": 6.73
  },
  {
    "text": "All ye shall be offended\nbecause of me this night:",
    "start": 305.16,
    "duration": 5.8
  },
  {
    "text": "for it is written, I\nwill smite the shepherd,",
    "start": 310.96,
    "duration": 5.292
  },
  {
    "text": "and the sheep of the flock\nshall be scattered abroad.",
    "start": 316.252,
    "duration": 2.208
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 318.46,
    "duration": 4.39
  },
  {
    "text": "Peter, James, and I followed\nHim further into the garden.",
    "start": 322.85,
    "duration": 5.87
  },
  {
    "text": "My soul is exceeding\nsorrowful, even unto death;",
    "start": 328.72,
    "duration": 9.595
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 338.315,
    "duration": 6.185
  },
  {
    "text": "tarry ye here,\nand watch with me.",
    "start": 344.5,
    "duration": 4.25
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 348.75,
    "duration": 12.87
  },
  {
    "text": "Abba,",
    "start": 361.62,
    "duration": 2.97
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 364.59,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "Father,",
    "start": 368.55,
    "duration": 4.455
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 373.005,
    "duration": 4.965
  },
  {
    "text": "all things are\npossible unto thee;",
    "start": 377.97,
    "duration": 4.325
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 382.295,
    "duration": 4.755
  },
  {
    "text": "take away this cup from me:",
    "start": 387.05,
    "duration": 5.164
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 392.214,
    "duration": 6.396
  },
  {
    "text": "nevertheless not my\nwill, but thine, be done.",
    "start": 398.61,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 404.93,
    "duration": 10.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Indeed, our spirits\nwere willing,",
    "start": 415.14,
    "duration": 3.158
  },
  {
    "text": "but our flesh was weak, for\nwe were heavy with sleep.",
    "start": 418.298,
    "duration": 7.013
  },
  {
    "text": "Sleepest thou?",
    "start": 425.311,
    "duration": 2.804
  },
  {
    "text": "couldest not thou\nwatch one hour?",
    "start": 428.115,
    "duration": 1.988
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 430.103,
    "duration": 7.728
  },
  {
    "text": "We did not comprehend\nthat the Son of God, who",
    "start": 437.831,
    "duration": 4.819
  },
  {
    "text": "we saw had the power\nto forgive sins,",
    "start": 442.65,
    "duration": 3.7
  },
  {
    "text": "was now offering\nHimself as payment",
    "start": 446.35,
    "duration": 3.57
  },
  {
    "text": "for the misdeeds of all mankind.",
    "start": 449.92,
    "duration": 4.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Unaware, we slept on.",
    "start": 454.19,
    "duration": 2.91
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 457.1,
    "duration": 6.89
  },
  {
    "text": "He was in great agony.",
    "start": 463.99,
    "duration": 4.53
  },
  {
    "text": "\"He prayed more\nearnestly: and his sweat",
    "start": 468.52,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": "was as it were great drops\nof blood falling down",
    "start": 472.08,
    "duration": 3.07
  },
  {
    "text": "to the ground.\"",
    "start": 475.15,
    "duration": 2.748
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 477.898,
    "duration": 34.502
  },
  {
    "text": "Whom seek ye?",
    "start": 512.4,
    "duration": 1.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Jesus of Nazareth.",
    "start": 513.82,
    "duration": 1.16
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 514.98,
    "duration": 9.58
  },
  {
    "text": "One of our own betrayed our\nLord to the rulers of the Jews.",
    "start": 524.56,
    "duration": 6.455
  },
  {
    "text": "[KISSES CHEEK]",
    "start": 531.015,
    "duration": 0.95
  },
  {
    "text": "Master.",
    "start": 531.965,
    "duration": 2.855
  },
  {
    "text": "Ye have brought\nthis man unto me,",
    "start": 534.82,
    "duration": 1.54
  },
  {
    "text": "as one that\nperverteth the people.",
    "start": 536.36,
    "duration": 1.81
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 538.17,
    "duration": 2.82
  },
  {
    "text": "I have examined him before\nyou, and find no fault",
    "start": 540.99,
    "duration": 3.66
  },
  {
    "text": "with this man touching those\nthings whereof you accuse him.",
    "start": 544.65,
    "duration": 5.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I have sent him to Herod.",
    "start": 550.03,
    "duration": 2.045
  },
  {
    "text": "He has found that nothing\nworthy of death has been done.",
    "start": 552.075,
    "duration": 4.985
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 557.06,
    "duration": 3.77
  },
  {
    "text": "I will therefore chastise\nhim, and release him.",
    "start": 560.83,
    "duration": 5.268
  },
  {
    "text": "[CROWD MURMURING]",
    "start": 566.098,
    "duration": 3.486
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 569.584,
    "duration": 3.496
  },
  {
    "text": "According to your custom\nat this time of year,",
    "start": 573.08,
    "duration": 3.32
  },
  {
    "text": "one prisoner shall be released.",
    "start": 576.4,
    "duration": 3.21
  },
  {
    "text": "Barabbas.",
    "start": 579.61,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Free Barabbas.",
    "start": 581.21,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "[CROWD CHEERING]",
    "start": 582.57,
    "duration": 3.115
  },
  {
    "text": "What shall I do then with\nJesus who is called the Christ?",
    "start": 585.685,
    "duration": 4.369
  },
  {
    "text": "Crucify him.",
    "start": 590.054,
    "duration": 2.46
  },
  {
    "text": "[CROWD CHANTING]",
    "start": 592.514,
    "duration": 1.476
  },
  {
    "text": "Crucify him!",
    "start": 593.99,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "No!",
    "start": 595.95,
    "duration": 0.5
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 596.45,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Please, spare my son!",
    "start": 601.37,
    "duration": 3.936
  },
  {
    "text": "[CROWD CHANTING]",
    "start": 605.306,
    "duration": 3.444
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 608.75,
    "duration": 6.93
  },
  {
    "text": "I am innocent of the blood of\nthis just person: see ye to it.",
    "start": 615.68,
    "duration": 7.98
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 623.66,
    "duration": 7.89
  },
  {
    "text": "[WOMEN CRYING]",
    "start": 631.55,
    "duration": 3.465
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 635.015,
    "duration": 14.85
  },
  {
    "text": "[HAMMER POUNDING]",
    "start": 649.865,
    "duration": 6.93
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 656.795,
    "duration": 7.995
  },
  {
    "text": "Even in His intense suffering,\nas He paid the final price",
    "start": 664.79,
    "duration": 4.91
  },
  {
    "text": "for us all, His\nthoughts were on others.",
    "start": 669.7,
    "duration": 5.18
  },
  {
    "text": "His final request of me was to\ncare for His beloved mother.",
    "start": 674.88,
    "duration": 6.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Behold thy mother!",
    "start": 681.68,
    "duration": 1.47
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 683.15,
    "duration": 3.43
  },
  {
    "text": "[THUNDER RUMBLING]",
    "start": 686.58,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Father, into thy hands\nI commend my spirit.",
    "start": 690.5,
    "duration": 7.185
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 697.685,
    "duration": 3.065
  },
  {
    "text": "It is finished.",
    "start": 700.75,
    "duration": 1.435
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 702.185,
    "duration": 4.495
  },
  {
    "text": "[THUNDER RUMBLING]",
    "start": 706.68,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 709.68,
    "duration": 35.095
  },
  {
    "text": "The darkness is past, and\nthe true light now shineth.",
    "start": 744.775,
    "duration": 3.845
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 748.62,
    "duration": 5.9
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the promise that He had\npromised us, even eternal life.",
    "start": 754.52,
    "duration": 7.631
  },
  {
    "text": "Mary.",
    "start": 762.151,
    "duration": 0.499
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 762.65,
    "duration": 7.28
  },
  {
    "text": "Rabboni.",
    "start": 769.93,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "For we beheld His glory.",
    "start": 771.93,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "Because of Him, we all shall\nlive again, for He is risen.",
    "start": 775.53,
    "duration": 8.79
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "start": 784.32,
    "duration": 17.744
  }
]